# Curated common Kali tools baked into the security edition (KALI_TOOLS=1).
# Installed from the pinned Kali repo at build time. Edit freely — one
# package per line, '#' comments ignored. These are mostly Kali-only tools
# (not in Debian); Debian-provided tools (nmap, wireshark, hydra, john,
# hashcat, sqlmap, aircrack-ng) already come from the 40-security stack.
metasploit-framework
burpsuite
radare2
exploitdb
seclists
wordlists
feroxbuster
ffuf
nikto
wpscan
dirb
wfuzz
netexec
responder
enum4linux-ng
dnsenum
amass
